The dean expresses gratitude to recruiters for their support as career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries. Career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops, and interview sign-up sheets fill with names as the day winds down. Meanwhile, a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. Outside, friends decompress on the quad, discussing which companies responded warmly.

Additionally, an alumni panel discusses how to prepare for technical interviews. A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session.
